Title: NLP Web Scraper
Description: Shiny app that uses the Claude API to translate natural language
    web scraping instructions into executable R code.  Supports static pages
    (rvest) and dynamic JavaScript-rendered pages (RSelenium).
Depends:
    shiny,
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    rvest,
    R.utils,
    bslib,
    DT
Suggests:
    RSelenium
